{"id":7601,"content":"<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">&nbsp; 中共《党员领导干部廉洁从政若干准则》，从</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1997</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年制定以来，<B>“</B>试行”了十三年，于日前发布了它修订以后的正式版。十三年的“试行”，究竟说明这样一种<B>“</B>准则”很有必要还是并无必要，发布机关未予解释，我倾向于后一答案。这倒不是因为我有什么统计证据说明十三年来从政诸公的“人均廉洁度”和“全员廉洁分子比”并未增加或者反而下降，<B>“</B>人均腐败度”和<B>“</B>全员腐败分子比”反而上升，尽管从每年中共中央纪委的会上最高领导人一次再次共十多次强调党内反腐败任务的<B>“</B>长期性艰巨性复杂性”，就已考验出它的效力或没有效力；我只是从准则条文里得出这个结论的，并且有把握地说，按照这样的条文，很难有助于以上统计指标变得可爱起来。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">我的理由如下：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">首先，它不是“党”纪。中共的党纪，是对作为<B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">中国工人阶级的先锋队，同时是中国人民和中华民族的先锋队”的中共党员的特别规范，而对于本准则所更加特别规范的“县（处）级以上”领导干部，自然要求更特别。可是这样的要求，</SPAN><B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">试行版”未作任何规定，</SPAN><B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">正式版”倒的确加有一段</SPAN><B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">总则”，作了原则要求：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; mso-para-margin-left: 2.0gd\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">党员领导干部必须具有共产主义远大理想和中国特色社会主义坚定信念，践行社会主义核心价值体系；必须坚持全心全意为人民服务的宗旨，立党为公、执政为民；必须在党员和人民群众中发挥表率作用，自重、自省、自警、自励；必须模范遵守党纪国法，清正廉洁，忠于职守，正确行使权力，始终保持职务行为的廉洁性；必须弘扬党的优良作风，求真务实，艰苦奋斗，密切联系群众。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">提出这样的要求，自然像个“先锋队”的样子。可是本准则的所有具体规定，从</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">禁止利用职权和职务上的影响谋取不正当利益”，到<B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">禁止脱离实际，弄虚作假，损害群众利益”，仅仅是不偷不骗不贪不占等等做人的基本准则，乃是一切公务人员，县团级以上或者以下，共产党员或非共产党员，民主人士或不民主人士，只要领取人民的税金过活，必须遵守底线。不犯以上错误，未必就是</SPAN><B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">先锋队”就践行了</SPAN><B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">核心价值体系”，而那些还不是</SPAN><B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">先锋队”、并不懂得或不赞成</SPAN><B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">核心价值体系”的非党员领导干部，也是绝对不允许</SPAN><B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">谋取不正当利益”和</SPAN><B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">弄虚作假”，越过这条底线的，这该是常识了吧？</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">其实本准则的种种规定，只是起码的行政规则，不是党纪而是政纪。如果必须制定这样的纪律，它也不应由中共中央向</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">县（团）级以上”党员干部、而应由国务院向全体公务员颁发。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; mso-para-margin-left: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">其次，它甚至不是单纯的</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">纪律”。上文有一句</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">如果必须制定这样的纪律”，是为以下的事实留下空间：它的很多规则，已经是现行的法律或者以法律的形式规定的纪律。首先，我国的《公务员法》的第五十三条规定，</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">公务员必须遵守纪律，不得有下列行为”：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> </FONT></SPAN></FONT><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">（六）弄虚作假，误导、欺骗领导和公众；</SPAN></FONT><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> <BR></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">（七）贪污、行贿、受贿，利用职务之便为自己或者他人谋取私利；</SPAN></FONT><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> <BR></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">（八）违反财经纪律，浪费国家资财；</SPAN></FONT><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> <BR></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">（十四）从事或者参与营利性活动，在企业或者其他营利性组织中兼任职务</SPAN></FONT><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">; <BR></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">比较中共的<B>“</B>准则”：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.5pt; mso-para-margin-left: 3.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">第八条</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> </FONT><A name=OLE_LINK1><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK1\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">禁止脱离实际，弄虚作假，损害群众利益和党群干群关系<SPAN style=\"COLOR: blue\">。</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK1\"></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.5pt; mso-para-margin-left: 3.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">第一条</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">禁止利用职权和职务上的影响谋取不正当利益。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> <o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 31.5pt; mso-para-margin-left: 3.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">第五条</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> <SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">禁止利用职权和职务上的影响为亲属及身边工作人员谋取利益。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 42pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; mso-para-margin-left: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 4.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">第六条</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">禁止讲排场、比阔气、挥霍公款、铺张浪费。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 52.5pt; mso-para-margin-left: 5.0gd\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">第二条</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">禁止私自从事营利性活动。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">两者意义重合，甚至连字句也重合。至于《公务员法》里所指<B>“</B>贪污、行贿、受贿”，<B>《</B>规范》里所指<B>“</B>利用职权……谋取不正当利益”，在《中华人民共和国刑法》里面已设<B>“</B>贪污贿赂罪”的专章禁止和惩戒，它是所有国民都必须遵守的法律。那么全体公务员必须遵守的纪律，全体国民必须遵守的法律，共产党对自己的<B>“</B>领导干部”还须重新规定一遍，这怎么说也不算<B>“</B>从严治党”、<B>“</B>保持先进性”的举措吧？假使这样的举措说明，中共自己如不把法律的禁止规定在党内重复规定一遍，它的<B>“</B>领导干部”就可以不遵守，那么它就违背了自己党章宣布的<B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">党必须在宪法和法律的范围内活动”：否则中共的领导干部也就该和所有党员及非党员干部一样遵守《公务员法》，和全体国民一样遵守《刑法》，那么这个准则里面的这些规定，究竟还有何用呢？</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">听说出台这种<B>“</B>准则”的意义，是它条文具体，<B>“</B>具有可操作性”。从十三年前的试行本，到现在的正式本子，的确设有相当具体的禁止条款，可是这正构成它的第三个缺陷：漏洞太多。须知<B>《</B>准则》规范的对象，乃是受人民之托手握公共权力的官员，按照现代法制的通则，对于他们，法无授权就不得作为，而与普通公民只须法无禁止就可以作为的原则相并立。所以，对于官员行为的规范是否<B>“</B>可操作”，不是看他是否触犯具体禁令，而是看他有无具体授权。十三年前的试行<B>“</B>准则”规定大小禁令</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">条，十三年后增加为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">51</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">条，其间还有</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2007</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年的<B>《</B>禁止利用职务之便谋取不正当利益规定》，其条文之繁琐，已经到了搞笑的程度。例如为了辨认何为<B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">通过赌博方式”收取请托（办事谋利）人的财物，细致入微地规定了对</SPAN><B>“</B><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black\">（</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">）赌博的背景、场合、时间、次数；（</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">）赌资来源；（</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">）其他赌博参与者有无事先通谋；（</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">）输赢钱物的具体情况和金额大小”的“因素进行判断”，看他该不该收钱。算不算正当。像这样不断增加</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">准则”的具体条款，恰恰把</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">无授权不得作为”变成</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">无禁止即可作为”。而公权力的本事要多大有多大，你禁止他一万条，他马上就想得出第一万零一条来；何况禁令越具体，越须靠列举，而列举总有</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">未尽事项”，留下无穷空子，按下葫芦起来瓢，禁不胜禁啊！</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">共产党对自己党员的期许和对党外世界的自诩，都是极高极美极理想的；而一部试行十几年后慎重定稿的党内纪律，居然不过就是起码的做人底线，就像在高雅富丽的俱乐部里优雅文明仪态万方的绅士淑女面前，高悬</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">不得随地大小便”的禁令，主其事者即使自己不觉脸红，也令任何自重的客人大不自在了。作者本人不才，也忝为中共党员。我每看到这类禁令时，总觉得羞愧难当，无地自容，难道我在本党的这些堂堂高官同志们，除了在党内如此严申做人底线，告诫他们这不准偷那不准抢，他们就不会做个起码的人吗！把这种“不得随地大小便”一类的“准则”，视为宝贝，望它“对于深入推进党风廉政建设和反腐败斗争，加强和改进新形势下党的建设，推动经济发展方式转变和保持经济平稳较快发展，夺取全面建设小康社会新胜利，开创中国特色社会主义事业新局面，具有重要现实意义和长远战略意义”，</SPAN></FONT><A style=\"mso-endnote-id: edn1\" title=\"\" href=\"http://www.yhcqw.com/admin2008/News/News_add.asp?ClassID=33BI6B6096DBEB3#_edn1\" name=_ednref1><SPAN class=MsoEndnoteReference><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">*</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></A><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">真叫人哭笑不得呢！</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">梳理起来，这种异常情况的出现，正是当前中共一部分（不好说其大小）干部的实际品格与党所宣称追求的崇高宗旨及自我认定出现强烈反差的反映，怪罪不得那些冥思苦想起草纪律条文的朋友们的。如果说中共作为革命政党的时候，它的党员素质与它所宣布的宗旨，尚能基本吻合，因而赢得人民的拥戴，取得了政权；而经过六十年的大权独揽，和它所宣传且实际取得的种种</SPAN><B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">辉煌”相并列的，就是这种权力的腐蚀作用，使党的公开宗旨和党的干部实际素质出现巨大裂痕。弥合这个裂痕，靠颁发禁令特别是重复已成法律和政纪的禁令，即使百条千条万条，实在于事难补；解决的办法乃在另一条路上，这就是毛泽东在延安窑洞里庄重宣告的那句名言：——</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">“我们已经找到了新路，这条新路就是民主，只有让人民监督政府，政府才不敢松懈。”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">这里说的<B>“</B>政府”，当然包含执政党的<B>“</B>党员领导干部”。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<DIV style=\"mso-element: endnote-list\"><BR clear=all><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT>\r\n<DIV style=\"mso-element: endnote\" id=edn1>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoFootnoteText><A style=\"mso-endnote-id: edn1\" title=\"\" href=\"http://www.yhcqw.com/admin2008/News/News_add.asp?ClassID=33BI6B6096DBEB3#_ednref1\" name=_edn1><SPAN class=MsoEndnoteReference><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT size=2 face=\"Times New Roman\">*</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></A><FONT size=2><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><SPAN lang=EN-US> <SPAN class=MsoFootnoteReference><SPAN style=\"mso-special-character: footnote\"><SPAN class=MsoFootnoteReference><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\" lang=EN-US>[i]</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">《认真贯彻落实〈中国共产党党员领导干部廉洁从政若干准则〉以党风廉政建设和反腐败斗争新成效取信于民》，《求是》</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2010</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman\">期。<BR><BR></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"><FONT color=#000000 size=3>（该文所表述的内容为作者本人观点，与《炎黄春秋》杂志及炎黄春秋网的观点和立场无关。）</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></SPAN></FONT>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoEndnoteText><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P></DIV></DIV>","title":"中共现行“廉政党纪”的效用问题","time":1277573400000}